nature teaches us.

1194
01:19:21.166 --> 01:19:22.750
Cheers!

1195
01:19:26.375 --> 01:19:29.125
I think our movie will bring
a big change to the cinema.

1196
01:19:30.375 --> 01:19:32.375
People have seen
a lot of innocuous films.

1197
