1226
01:20:51.750 --> 01:20:53.625
Make a peg for the guy.

1227
01:20:54.500 --> 01:20:55.625
Forgive me

1228
01:20:56.000 --> 01:20:57.250
I don't drink.
- Manu.

1229
01:20:57.666 --> 01:20:59.625
Room.
