1369
01:31:08.625 --> 01:31:13.166
Anyways. I suffocate being
around greedy and mean people.

1370
01:31:13.875 --> 01:31:15.875
I am very happy with what
I am and wherever I am.

1371
01:31:17.750 --> 01:31:18.541
Goodbye.

